[69.164526, "o", "\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K\u001b[1A\u001b[K \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m __tests__/commands/start.test.ts \u001b[2m(\u001b[22m\u001b[2m59 tests\u001b[22m\u001b[2m | \u001b[22m\u001b[33m58 skipped\u001b[39m\u001b[2m)\u001b[22m\u001b[33m 433\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mincludes workflow examples in start help\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses single project when no arg given\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses explicit project arg when given\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22merrors when explicit project not found\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22merrors when multiple projects and no arg\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22merrors when no projects configured\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — project resolution\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfalls back to managed staging config when AO_CONFIG_PATH points to a miss"]
[69.170622, "o", "ing file\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mreuses existing clone and generates config\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mclones repo via gh when gh auth is available\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfalls back to git clone when gh is unavailable\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses existing config when repo already has agent-orchestrator.yaml\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mresolves correct project when existing config has multiple projects\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — URL argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfails on clone error with descriptive message\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — local path argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22madds new local-path projects to staging instead of production\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — local path argument\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mrepairs an invalid staging symlink before onboarding a local path\r\n   \u001b"]
[69.207099, "o", "[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — browser open waits for port\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mcalls waitForPortAndOpen with orchestrator URL and AbortSignal\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — browser open waits for port\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips browser open and lifecycle with --no-dashboard --no-orchestrator\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — browser open waits for port\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips browser open but still starts lifecycle with --no-dashboard alone\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mshows reused messaging when strategy is reuse and metadata marks the session reused\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfalls back to attach messaging when strategy is reuse but metadata is missing\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is delete\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy displa"]
[69.224786, "o", "y\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is ignore\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is delete-new\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is ignore-new\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — orchestrator session strategy display\u001b[2m > \u001b[22muses attach messaging when strategy is kill-previous\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstops orchestrator session and dashboard\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mhandles missing orchestrator session gracefully\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdefaults to NOT purge OpenCode session when stopping orchestrator\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpasses purge flag when stopping orchestrator with --purge-session\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when project pat"]
[69.259813, "o", "h resolves to the main repo\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstarts normally when project path is NOT the main repo\r\n   \u001b[33m\u001b[2m✓\u001b[22m\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows the main repo when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 3) (bd-cj5s) \u001b[33m 420\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when local path argument resolves to the main repo (Site 2) (bd-cj5s)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows local path argument when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 2) (bd-cj5s)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when no-argument start cwd resolves to the main repo (Site 4) (bd-cj5s)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows no-argument start cwd when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 4) (bd-cj5s)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m s"]
[69.285939, "o", "tart command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when URL start target path resolves to the main repo (Site 1) (bd-cj5s)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows URL start when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 1) (bd-cj5s)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop does NOT unregister running.json\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop leaves the project in running.json (parent is still polling)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop only kills sessions for the named project\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfull stop (no arg) still kills parent and dashboard\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop records last-stop with correct project scope\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start comman"]
[69.302983, "o", "d — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mao start <project> while daemon alive: non-TTY caller exits without spawning second dashboard\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — autoCreateConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mgenerates config with empty notifiers array (no desktop notifier added by default)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits immediately for non-TTY caller when AO is already running\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits when human caller selects 'quit'\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpath arg already registered + running: opens dashboard without prompting and does not mutate YAML\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpath arg unregistered + AO running: registers in global config and spawns orchestrator without showing the menu\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22moffers t"]
[69.312776, "o", "o add cwd when AO is running and cwd is an unregistered git repo\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits when human caller selects 'open'\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mkills existing process and continues when human caller selects 'restart'\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstarts lifecycle and completes without error when --no-dashboard is used\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mcreates new orchestrator entry when human caller selects 'new'\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdoes not mutate YAML when non-TTY caller detects already running (path arg)\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — path-based deduplication in addProjectToConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips addProjectToConfig when path arg matches an existing project\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — path-based deduplication in addProjectToConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdeduplicates vi"]
[69.366003, "o", "a addProjectToConfig when path exists under a different name\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — global registry mutations\u001b[2m > \u001b[22madds a project to the global registry and writes behavior to the repo-local config\r\n   \u001b[2m\u001b[90m↓\u001b[39m\u001b[22m start command — global registry mutations\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mwrites interactive agent overrides to the repo-local config when using the global registry\r\n"]
