[155.648319, "o", "y\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdefaults to NOT purge OpenCode session when stopping orchestrator\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m stop command\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpasses purge flag when stopping orchestrator with --purge-session\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when project path resolves to the main repo\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstarts normally when project path is NOT the main repo\u001b[32m 14\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows the main repo when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 3) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 6\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when local path argument resolves to the main repo (Site 2) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows local path arg"]
[155.648561, "o", "ument when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 2) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 262\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when no-argument start cwd resolves to the main repo (Site 4) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows no-argument start cwd when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 4) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mthrows when URL start target path resolves to the main repo (Site 1) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mallows URL start when --allow-main-repo flag is set (Site 1) (bd-cj5s)\u001b[32m 3\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop does NOT unregister running.json\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop leaves the pr"]
[155.648807, "o", "oject in running.json (parent is still polling)\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop only kills sessions for the named project\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mfull stop (no arg) still kills parent and dashboard\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mtargeted stop records last-stop with correct project scope\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — main repo guard (bd-8gld)\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mao start <project> while daemon alive: non-TTY caller exits without spawning second dashboard\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — autoCreateConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mgenerates config with empty notifiers array (no desktop notifier added by default)\u001b[32m 7\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits immediately for non-TTY caller when AO is already running\u001b["]
[155.64899, "o", "32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits when human caller selects 'quit'\u001b[32m 1\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpath arg already registered + running: opens dashboard without prompting and does not mutate YAML\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[33m\u001b[2m✓\u001b[22m\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mpath arg unregistered + AO running: registers in global config and spawns orchestrator without showing the menu \u001b[33m 854\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22moffers to add cwd when AO is running and cwd is an unregistered git repo\u001b[32m 31\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mexits when human caller selects 'open'\u001b[32m 77\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — already-running detection\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mkills existing process and continues when human caller selects 'restart'\u001b["]
[155.650341, "o", "32m 7\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mstarts lifecycle and completes without error when --no-dashboard is used\u001b[32m 2\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mcreates new orchestrator entry when human caller selects 'new'\u001b[32m 171\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m no-dashboard keepalive\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdoes not mutate YAML when non-TTY caller detects already running (path arg)\u001b[32m 11\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — path-based deduplication in addProjectToConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mskips addProjectToConfig when path arg matches an existing project\u001b[32m 21\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — path-based deduplication in addProjectToConfig\u001b[2m > \u001b[22mdeduplicates via addProjectToConfig when path exists under a different name\u001b[32m 204\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n   \u001b[32m✓\u001b[39m start command — global registry mutations\u001b[2m > \u001b[22madds a project to the global registry and writes behavior to the repo-local config\u001b[32m 82\u001b[2mms\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\r\n "]
